text: Albert Späni (born 24 December 1927) is a Swiss former sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1927 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Swiss male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Switzerland Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from the canton of Schwyz
